OL,3,CSynedd Election: A fragmented and
OL,4,Cpolarised multi-party contest
OL,6,FCrucial elections are taking place
OL,7,Ftomorrow - local polls across England,
OL,8,Fand devolved elections in Scotland and
OL,9,FWales. By any reckoning, a huge amount
OL,10,Fwill be at stake when voting starts,
OL,11,Fnowhere more so than in Wales, for so
OL,12,Flong a Labour stronghold, as ITV News
OL,13,FWales Reporter Rhys Williams explains
OL,15,FWelsh politics is entering unfamiliar
OL,16,Fterritory.
OL,18,FFor decades, elections here have been
OL,19,Fa contest between the Labour Party and
OL,20,Fits challengers - primarily the
OL,21,FConservatives and Plaid Cymru.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
