OL,3,CSynedd Election: A fragmented and
OL,4,Cpolarised multi-party contest
OL,6,FOf the six devolved elections to date,
OL,7,Fthose two parties have been runners up
OL,8,Fthree times each.
OL,10,FThose days look to be over.
OL,12,FIn their place is a more fragmented
OL,13,Fand polarised multi-party contest.
OL,15,FAs political scientist Professor Jane
OL,16,FGreen points out, polling data from
OL,17,Facross the UK shows this is a shift
OL,18,Fbeing played out in all four nations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
