OL,3,CSynedd Election: A fragmented and
OL,4,Cpolarised multi-party contest
OL,6,FWales reflects that broader trend but
OL,7,Fwith its own distinct features. Here
OL,8,Fit's Plaid Cymru along with Reform UK
OL,9,Fchallenging Labour's historic
OL,10,Fdominance.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
