OL,3,CSynedd Election: A fragmented and
OL,4,Cpolarised multi-party contest
OL,6,FLabour are defending a century-long
OL,7,Fwinning streak in Wales, with the
OL,8,Fmessage that only a party with
OL,9,Fexperience in government can provide
OL,10,Fthe stability needed during difficult
OL,11,Feconomic times.
OL,13,FPlaid Cymru say they will fight for a
OL,14,Ffairer funding deal for Wales while
OL,15,Fpromising to turn around Wales'
OL,16,Fflagging public services. The unknown
OL,17,Fquantity is Reform UK, who are
OL,18,Fpromising to cut income tax as well as
OL,19,Fcivil service numbers by 10%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
