OL,3,CSynedd Election: A fragmented and
OL,4,Cpolarised multi-party contest
OL,6,FThis will be the first Senedd election
OL,7,Ffought under a new, more proportional
OL,8,Fsystem, with 6 members being elected
OL,9,Fin 16 large constituencies.
OL,11,FSmall changes in support (perhaps just
OL,12,Fa few hundred votes in a
OL,13,Fconstituency), could have a
OL,14,Fdisproportionate impact on how many
OL,15,Frepresentatives each party returns.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
