PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778148401
OL,3,CSynedd Election: A fragmented and
OL,4,Cpolarised multi-party contest
OL,6,FIn particular, Welsh Labour, the Welsh
OL,7,FConservatives and the Green Party are
OL,8,Fpolling at a level where a couple of
OL,9,Fpercentage point differences either
OL,10,Fway may have a significant impact on
OL,11,Fthe number of seats they could win.
OL,13,FWith no party likely to win a majority
OL,14,Funder this system, The Green Party
OL,15,Fbelieve they will finally make a
OL,16,Fbreakthrough in Wales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
