OL,3,CSynedd Election: A fragmented and
OL,4,Cpolarised multi-party contest
OL,6,FTheir leader says he is ready to be
OL,7,Fthe kingmakers after the election and
OL,8,Fis likely to demand any Plaid-led
OL,9,Fgovernment to prioritise rent freezes,
OL,10,Fand potentially rent controls.
OL,12,FLike Labour, Wales' other established
OL,13,Fparties are still hungry for votes.
OL,14,FThe Welsh Conservatives insist they
OL,15,Fcan win seats all over the country
OL,16,Fand, like Reform UK, are promising to
OL,17,Fcut income tax by 1p.
OL,19,FPolls consistently show the Welsh
OL,20,FLiberal Democrats struggling to make
OL,21,Fup ground.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
