OL,3,CSynedd Election: A fragmented and
OL,4,Cpolarised multi-party contest
OL,6,FLeader Jane Dodds, the sole Lib Dem in
OL,7,Fthe previous parliament, says she's
OL,8,Fdetermined not to be "billy no mates"
OL,9,Fthis time. Her campaign has
OL,10,Fprioritised social care.
OL,12,FThis is a Senedd election unlike any
OL,13,Fwe've seen before. While the campaign
OL,14,Fis nearly over, a more disruptive and
OL,15,Fcontentious politics looks likely to
OL,16,Fstay.
OL,18,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,19,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,20,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,21,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
